Package: Vtiger
Type: Package
Title: Provides R integration with Vtiger CRM System
Version: 0.1
Date: 2014-07-05
Author: Richard Morris <vtiger.r.package@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Richard Morris <vtiger.r.package@gmail.com>
Description: Vtiger is an open source CRM system. This
    package provides for CRUD integration between Vtiger and
    R. This package may be useful for anyone wanting to
    integrate customer/personal information with R
    functionality - e.g. Emailing (with the help of sendmailR)
    analysis/reports generated in R to a Vtiger client
    distribution list.
License: GPL-2
Imports:
    digest,RCurl,rjson
